                    </div>
                    <span>I have always admired Stephen King throughout his long and successful writing career.  When I saw this book, I decided to read it as well.  I must say that this title only further enhanced my admiration for the man.
<br />
<br />I found very useful advice and insight for any aspiring author.  The advice contained in this book makes it worth the price.  However, it doesn't stop there.  Stephen King walks us through how his career began and the struggles he had in getting there and staying there.
<br />
<br />Mr. King even comments on the accident in Maine that left him with serious injuries.  Aspiring writer or just a Stephen King fan, this book is for all of you.</span>
                  
              
